@startuml
title CosX Compliance Agent - POC Architecture

skinparam rectangle {
    BackgroundColor white
    BorderColor #333333
}

actor "Compliance\nOfficer" as CO
actor "Investment\nManager" as PM

rectangle "Input Layer" {
    usecase "Compliance\nQuestion" as Q
    usecase "Upload\nFactsheet PDF" as U
}

rectangle "Knowledge Base (RAG)" {
    database "Vector DB" as VDB
    card "Code on CIS\n(2025.11 Rev)\n~300-500 pages" as CIS
    card "SFA Offers\nof Investment\n~100 pages" as SFA
    card "MAS Pointers\non CIS\n~30-50 pages" as MP
    card "IMAS Code\nBest Practices\n~50-80 pages" as IMAS
}

rectangle "Reasoning Layer" {
    card "Claude LLM\n+ Retrieval" as LLM
    card "Compliance\nQ&A Engine" as QA
    card "Document\nReview Engine" as DR
}

rectangle "Output Layer" {
    card "Answer with\nRegulation Citations" as ANS
    card "Structured\nReview Report\nCritical/Warning/Pass" as RPT
}

CO --> Q
CO --> U
PM --> Q

Q --> LLM
U --> DR

CIS --> VDB
SFA --> VDB
MP --> VDB
IMAS --> VDB

VDB --> LLM
LLM --> QA
LLM --> DR

QA --> ANS
DR --> RPT

ANS --> CO
RPT --> CO

note right of VDB
    Chunking Strategy:
    Split by Section/Paragraph
    Preserve hierarchy
    Tag with metadata:
    - Regulation name
    - Section number
    - Revision date
end note

note right of RPT
    Review Output:
    [C-01] Critical: Missing disclaimer
    Rule: Code on CIS, App 1, S2.1
    [W-01] Warning: Fee incomplete
    Rule: Code on CIS, S8.2
    [P-01] Passed: Risk statement OK
end note

@enduml
